            <section class="inner-content">
                 <p><img src="content/images/2013/Dec/kraken-1.png" alt="" /></p>

<p>A lightweight, mobile-first boilerplate for front-end web developers. Kraken is now powered by Sass for easier customization.</p>

<h2 id="justtheessentials">Just the Essentials</h2>

<p>Designed to be lightweight and style agnostic, Kraken includes just the essentials.</p>

<h2 id="cssreset">CSS Reset</h2>

<p>Ensure cross-browser compatibility.</p>

<h2 id="responsivegrid">Responsive Grid</h2>

<p>A responsive, mobile-first grid.</p>

<h2 id="typography">Typography</h2>

<p>A well-designed, fluid typographic scale.</p>

<h2 id="buttons">Buttons</h2>

<p>Easily style links and buttons with CSS.</p>

<h2 id="forms">Forms</h2>

<p>Basic styling for common form elements.</p>

<h2 id="addons">Add-Ons</h2>

<p>Add functionality with optional add-ons.</p>

<p>Learn more at <a href="http://cferdinandi.github.io/kraken/index.html">Kraken</a>.</p>
            </section>

